				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-karren" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5968578); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5968578&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224094" alt="Dr Karren" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5968578)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-karren" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5968578); return false;" >Dr Karren</a></span> <span class="odate time_1579008022 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">14 Jan 2020 13:20</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4468387">
									

<p>Well as of writing this, there are a total of 14 Main List Apollyon SCPs (if you count SCP-001 Proposals) Here's a list&#8230;(This will be a list of main list Apollyon Class SCPs and if more get added to the Main List, they will be added on this post).</p>
<ul>
<li>SCP-3999 ([<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3999">http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3999</a>]) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2527320); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2527320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1581817578" alt="LordStonefish" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2527320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2527320); return false;">LordStonefish</a></span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>S.D. Locke's Proposal ([<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/shaggydredlocks-proposal">http://www.scp-wiki.net/shaggydredlocks-proposal</a>]) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1722371); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1722371&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1581817578" alt="Shaggydredlocks" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1722371)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shaggydredlocks" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1722371); return false;">Shaggydredlocks</a></span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Meta Ike's Proposal ([<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/jack-ike-s-proposal-i">http://www.scp-wiki.net/jack-ike-s-proposal-i</a>]) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jack-ike" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1618170); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1618170&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1581817578" alt="Jack Ike" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1618170)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jack-ike" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1618170); return false;">Jack Ike</a></span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
